                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-966-18681026 t18681026-966-punishment-68"></join>Eighteen Months Imprisonment</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Common Serjeant</hi>,</p>
